show.title: My Junior Sister Went Mad
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/5ceZ9a
show.description: Once a devoted disciple of Kunlun Mountain, NANCY faces betrayal from her sect, rejection from her master, and humiliation by her peers. When her loyalty is shattered and her spirit crushed, she declares war on those who wronged her—including her so-called junior sister, SONIYA. My Junior Sister Went Mad is a fierce tale of vengeance, broken bonds, and a woman reclaiming her power at any cost.
